<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='text-align:center'><b><span
style='font-size:16.0pt;font-family:標楷體'>中華科技大學教師教學評鑑施行細則</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=right style='text-align:right'><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:10.0pt'>94</span><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
標楷體'>年</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt'>2</span><span
style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:標楷體'>月</span><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:10.0pt'>15</span><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
標楷體'>日校務會議通過</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=right style='margin-right:5.0pt;text-align:right'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt'>96</span><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
 標楷體'>年</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt'>2</span><span
 style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:標楷體'>月</span><span lang=EN-US
 style='font-size:10.0pt'>5</span><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
 標楷體'>日</span><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:標楷體'>校務會議通過</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:24.0pt;text-indent:-24.0pt;line-height:
22.0pt'><span style='font-family:標楷體'>一、</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>中華科技大學（以下簡稱本校）為提升教師教學品質，依據本校教師教學服務研究評鑑辦法訂定教學評鑑施行細則（以下簡稱本細則）。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:24.0pt;text-indent:-24.0pt;line-height:
22.0pt'><span style='font-family:標楷體'>二、本細則以計分之方式進行評量，基本分數為七十分，最高分為一百分。評量範圍及標準包含下列事項：</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:9.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:0cm;
margin-left:43.65pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-19.55pt'><span
lang=EN-US>(一)</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>學生專題製作或專題研究指導</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:48.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>1.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>帶領或指導學生參加教學、研究或專題製作競賽者加</span><span
lang=EN-US>1</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>&#12316;</span><span lang=EN-US>10</span><span
style='font-family:標楷體'>分。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:48.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>2.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>申請通過國科會大專生專題計畫者加</span><span
lang=EN-US>3</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>分。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:48.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>3.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>輔導學生取得專業證照，加</span><span
lang=EN-US>0.2</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>&#12316;</span><span lang=EN-US>10</span><span
style='font-family:標楷體'>分。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:60.0pt;text-indent:-12.0pt;line-height:
22.0pt'><span lang=EN-US>4.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>指導學生參</span><span
style='font-family:標楷體'>加本校金華獎競賽，第一名加</span><span lang=EN-US>3</span><span
style='font-family:標楷體'>分、第二名加</span><span lang=EN-US>2</span><span
style='font-family:標楷體'>分、第三名加</span><span lang=EN-US>1</span><span
style='font-family:標楷體'>分。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:9.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:0cm;
margin-left:43.5pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-19.5pt'><span lang=EN-US>(二)</span><span
style='font-family:標楷體'>教學教材之製作</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:48.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>1.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>錄製</span><span lang=EN-US>e-learning</span><span
style='font-family:標楷體'>課程，當年度加</span><span lang=EN-US>1</span><span
style='font-family:標楷體'>&#12316;</span><span lang=EN-US>5</span><span
style='font-family:標楷體'>分。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:60.0pt;text-indent:-12.0pt;line-height:
22.0pt'><span lang=EN-US>2.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>建立教師個人教學網頁、教材或教具，經審核通過獲補助者，當年度每案加</span><span
lang=EN-US>1</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>分，最高上限</span><span lang=EN-US>3</span><span
style='font-family:標楷體'>分。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:48.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>3.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>取得與授課科目相關之當年度國家性專業證照，乙級加</span><span
lang=EN-US>3</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>分，甲級加</span><span lang=EN-US>5</span><span
style='font-family:標楷體'>分。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:9.0pt;text-indent:24.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>(</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>三</span><span lang=EN-US>) </span><span
style='font-family:標楷體'>上課出勤情形</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:48.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>1.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>經學校排定監考而無故未到，每次扣</span><span
lang=EN-US>1</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>分。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:48.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>2.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>未事先報備而私下變更上課地點，每次扣</span><span
lang=EN-US>1</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>分。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:60.0pt;text-indent:-12.0pt;line-height:
22.0pt'><span lang=EN-US>3.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>未依規定程序辦理調、補課，或申請經核准後，未依規定時間完成補課，每次扣</span><span
lang=EN-US>1</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>分。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:48.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>4.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>上課遲到早退、每次扣</span><span
lang=EN-US>1</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>分。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:48.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>5.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>留校課輔時間無故未到者，每次扣</span><span
lang=EN-US>1</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>分。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:9.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:0cm;
margin-left:43.65pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-19.55pt'><span
lang=EN-US>(四)</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>教學評量調查結果</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:61.9pt;text-indent:-12.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>1.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>各科教學評量調查低於</span><span
lang=EN-US>3.0</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>，且未依規定繳交「教學評量回應及可能之改善</span><span
style='font-family:標楷體'>方法填寫表」者，每科目扣</span><span lang=EN-US>1</span><span
style='font-family:標楷體'>分，已按規定繳交者，不予扣分。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:61.9pt;text-indent:-12.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>2.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>每學期之總平均分數小於</span><span
lang=EN-US>2.0</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>時，經查確有不當之上課缺失者（私自停課、談論與課程無關事務<span
lang=EN-US>……）扣</span></span><span lang=EN-US>5</span><span style='font-family:
標楷體'>分；經查無不當上課缺失者，不予扣分。若屬重大教學缺失，得提報各級教評會審議。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:9.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:0cm;
margin-left:43.65pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-19.55pt'><span
lang=EN-US>(五)</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>其他教學事項</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:60.0pt;text-indent:-12.0pt;line-height:
20.0pt'><span lang=EN-US>1.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>其他足以證明有關教學表現優劣事件，經校教評會評定，其加扣分上下限為</span><span
lang=EN-US>1</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>&#12316;</span><span lang=EN-US>20</span><span
style='font-family:標楷體'>分。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:60.0pt;text-indent:-12.0pt;line-height:
22.0pt'><span lang=EN-US>2.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>成績經公告後，因教師核算或登錄疏忽更改成績者，更改一名學生扣</span><span
lang=EN-US>1</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>分，以</span><span lang=EN-US>5</span><span
style='font-family:標楷體'>分為上限。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:48.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>3.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>未依規定時間內繳交期中考、期末考成績，每科目扣</span><span
lang=EN-US>1</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>分，並應累計扣分。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:48.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>4.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>獲選優良教學教師者，每名加</span><span
lang=EN-US>5</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>分。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:48.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>5.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>未依規定繳交課程大綱，每科目扣</span><span
lang=EN-US>1</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>分。</span><span lang=EN-US>&nbsp;
</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:22.0pt'><span style='font-family:標楷體'>三、本細則經校務會議通過後，陳請校長核定後公布實施，修正時亦同。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-US>&nbsp;</span></p>

